relevant_findings.general: A&O (Alert and Oriented), NAD (No Acute Distress)
relevant_findings.HEENT: No scleral icterus, mucus membranes moist
relevant_findings.CV: RRR (Regular Rate and Rhythm), No M/G/R (Murmurs, Gallops, Rhonchi)
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, No W/R/R (Wheezes, Rales, Rhonchi)
relevant_findings.abdomen: Soft, nondistended, tender to palpation in RLQ, no rebound or guarding, normoactive bowel sounds, no palpable masses
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused
